createListOfCombinations

public static java.util.Vector<java.util.Vector<Point>> createListOfCombinations(java.util.Vector<Point> pointList)
Method that creates list of all combinations of points from given list. E.g. if A, B and C are points that make passed in list of points, then this method returns following list with all combinations:
A
B
C
A B
A C
B C
A B C

Parameters:
pointList - List of points - there are no duplicates in this list
Returns:
List of all combinations of given points; null in case of error

getPointListKey

public static java.lang.String getPointListKey(java.util.Vector<Point> pointList)
Method that generates unique string key for list of points. Key is list of point labels ordered in ascending order, e.g. {B, A, D} has key "ABD".

Parameters:
pointList - List of points
Returns:
String key of point list
